ol.li:
The built-in CSS already has the following rule defined that activates
          hyphenation:*[class ~= "topic/table"] {
    hyphens: auto;
}To
          disable table hyphenation, add the following in your customization
          CSS:*[class ~= "topic/table"] {
    hyphens: none;
}

To prevent certain elements from being hyphenated, use
          hyphens:none. The following example excludes the
          keyword elements from being
        hyphenated:*[class ~= "topic/keyword"] {
    hyphens: none;
}
